== Taariikh ==
[[File:Welcome to AU.jpeg|thumb|Tiirka "Soo Dhawaynta" Jaamacada Camuud.]]

Markii ay dhaceen dagaaladii sokeeye ee dalka [[Soomaaliya]], waxa buruburay dhamaan machadadii waxbarasho ee xiligaa jiray sidaa daraadeed waxa loo baahday machado waxbarsho oo aad u sareeya, markaa sanadkii 1996 waxa la asaasay Jaamacada Camuud<ref>'''1996 waxa la asaasay Jaamacada Camuud'''</ref> si ay u noqoto il waxbarasho, xiligaa waxa loo magacaabay Jaamcada Camuud gudoomiyaheega [[Prof. Saleebaan Axmed Guuleed]] ilaa imikana haya xilka gudoomiyanimada jaamacada.<ref>"[[Prof. Saleebaan Axmed Guuleed]]"</ref><ref name="Maamulka Jaamacada">{{cite web
 |title=The Administration Of Amoud University
 |url=http://amouduniversity.org/index.php/about/history-and-background}}</ref>}}

[[Sanad|Sanadkii 1996dii]] ayaa guuto [[aqoon]]yahano, waxgarad, cuqaal, [[ganacsi|ganacsato]] iyo qurbo-joog reer [[Awdal]] ahi isla garteen ineey aasaasaan jaamacad waxbarsho, taasi oo laga hirgeliyay deegaanka [[Camuud]], ee waqooyi bari magaalada [[Borama]]. Dadkii abaabulka jaamacada waday waxay isla garteen in dhismaha dugsiga sare ee Camuud oo wakhtigaasi shaqo gabay, laga dhigo hooyga [[Jaamacada Camuud]].<ref name="Diploomka 2da Sano ee Jaamacada">{{cite web
 |title=The Two Year Diploma Of Amoud University
 |url=http://www.amouduniversity.org/index.php/departments-and-units-administrations}}</ref>
 
Dhinaca kale, [[sanad|sanadkii 1998dii]] ayaa la bilaabay casharada jaamacada, ka dib markii dib u habeyn lagu sameeyay dhismaha jaamacada oo 5 km waqooyi bari ka xiga magaalada Borama. Intaas waxaa dheer, agabka tiro yar iyo gaadiid kooban ayaa lagu wareejiyay maamulka jaamacada.<ref>"[[sanad|sanadkii 1998dii]] ayaa la bilaabay casharada jaamacada"</ref> 

Si kastaba ha ahaatee, bishii Julaay horaanteedii ee sanadkii 1998dii ayaa 66 ardey iyo sadex professor lagu bilaabay Jaamacada Camuud. Wakhtigani shaqaalaha, ardeyda iyo [[shidaal]]ka [[gaadiid]]ka jaamacadu waxay ku tiirsanayd deeqo ey jaamacadu ka heli jirtey [[ganacsi|ganacsatada]] iyo qurbo-joogta u dhalatay gobolka [[Awdal]].<ref>"shaqaalaha, ardeyda iyo [[shidaal]]ka [[gaadiid]]ka jaamacadu waxay ku tiirsanayd deeqo"</ref> 

Dadaal badan iyo dhiiranaan dheer ka dib, [[sanad|sanadkii 2003da]] wixii ka dambeeysay jaamacadu waxay noqotay mid ayadu ku istaagtey lugaheeda, sababtoo ah ardey badan ayaa ku soo biirtey jaamacada, isla markaana agab fiican ayay heshay jaamacadu. 
Sanadkii 2012ka Jaamacada Camuud waxay baahisay ineey bixiso 9 waaxood (faculty) oo waxbarsho ah; ay ka qalinjabiyeen kumanaan ardey ah; ay wakhtigaas diiwaan gashanaayeen tiro kor u dhaafaysay 4,000 ardey; tirada shaqaalaha, macalimiinta, iyo professoradu yihiin 238 qof; isla markaana ay leedahay in ka badan 30 gaadiid ah oo iskugu jira basas waawayn, caasiyo iyo gawaadhi kale.<ref name="Kuliyada Waxbarasho ee Jaamacada">{{cite web
 |title=The Faculty Of Education Of Amoud University
 |url=http://www.amouduniversity.org/index.php/about/history-and-background}}</ref> 

Jaamacada Camuud waxa lagu tiriyay 3000 machad ee ugu waxbarashada fiican caalamka.

